23#include "mpfr-impl.h"
24
25/* default is IEEE double precision, i.e. 53 bits */
26MPFR_THREAD_VAR (mpfr_prec_t, __gmpfr_default_fp_bit_precision,
27 IEEE_DBL_MANT_DIG)
28
29void
30mpfr_set_default_prec (mpfr_prec_t prec)
31{
32 MPFR_ASSERTN (MPFR_PREC_COND (prec));
33 __gmpfr_default_fp_bit_precision = prec;
34}
35
36#undef mpfr_get_default_prec
37mpfr_prec_t
38mpfr_get_default_prec (void)
39{
40 return __gmpfr_default_fp_bit_precision;
41}
